                <form>
                  <legend>Add Commission</legend>
                  <p>
                    Create a new commission. When applicable, specify an involved artist, the customer, a genre, and a medium. 
                    Indicate the status of the commission, the date the commission was requested, and, if finished, the date it
                    was completed. Input the price.
                  </p>
                  <label for="artists">Artists</label>
                  <input type="text" id="artists" name="artists">
                  <label for="customers">Customers</label>
                  <input type="text" id="customers" name="customers">

